        <div n="M63692D2" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">P<hi rend="SMALL-CAPS">LEARACA</hi></hi> na Ruàrcach</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-2"> Accuìmhne auile dhuine,</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-3"> Da ttiucaidh da bhifaicfeah</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-4"> S'da ccluinfeadh go fóill.</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-5"> Seacht bhfithchead muc,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-6"> Mart agus càora,</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-7"> Da ccasgairt don ghasraidh,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-8"> Gach àon, lò,</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-9"> Na cèada pàl uisge-beatha,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-10"> 'Sna meadra dha liónadh,</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-11"> Ag èirghe air maidin,</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-12"> Is againn a bhi an spòirt,</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-13"> Do briseadh mo phiopasa,</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-14"> Sladamh mo phócafa,</l><l n="15" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-15"> Guideath mo bhrísdesi,</l><l n="16" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-16"> Loisgeadh mo chlócasa.</l><l n="17" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-17"> Caill me mo bhirréad,</l><l n="18" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-18"> Mfallainn ís mfilleád;</l><l n="19" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-19"> O dimigh na gairead,</l><l n="20" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-20"> Ar sheacht mbeannacht lèo,</l><l n="21" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-21"> Spreag air ann cclairfigh sinn,</l><l n="22" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-22"> Seinn an Pléaráca sin,</l><l n="23" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-23"> Prap dhuinn sgáird don digh sin:</l><l n="24" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-24"> A, sì so, an chuirm chòir.</l><l n="25" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-25"> Lucht leanmhuna na Ruarcach</l><l n="26" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-26"> Ag crathadh a ccleitighe,</l><l n="27" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-27"> Tra chúala siad turman,</l><l n="28" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-28"> Is troipleásg a cheoil.</l><l n="29" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-29"> Gan aire air a ccoisreagadh,</l><l n="30" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-30"> Ag eìrgha as a leapacha;</l><l n="31" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-31"> Is a bhean feín ar leathlamih</l><l n="32" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-32"> Ag gach aon don choip.</l><l n="33" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-33"> Budh láidir an seasamh,</l><l n="34" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-34"> Don talamh, bhi fúthfa;</l><l n="35" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-35"> Gan réabadh le sodar</l><l n="36" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-36"> Is glugar ann gach bróig.</l><l n="37" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-37"> Sláinte agus saoghal chugad</l><l n="38" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-38"> Mhaoileachluin ui Aonagain,</l><l n="39" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-39"> Dar mo laimh is maith adhamhsas tu,</l><l n="40" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-40"> A Mhairsillnì Griodagain.</l><l n="41" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-41"> Sùd ort a mhathair</l><l n="42" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-42"> Go raibh maith agad a Phadruig,</l><l n="43" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-43"> Sgag thusa an sgá a sin</l><l n="44" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-44"> Siós an do sgóig.</l><l n="45" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-45"> Craith fúinn an tsráideóg fin,</l><l n="46" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-46"> Leathnoigh cruinn an chátheóg fin,</l><l n="47" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-47"> An bugsa sin Aine is</l><l n="48" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-48"> Graideóg le na ól.</l><l n="49" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-49"> Athair na ngrasa cé be,</l><l n="50" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-50"> Chifeadh an ghasraidh,</l><l n="51" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-51"> Tar lionadh a cecroicne,</l><l n="52" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-52"> Is ar lasadh san ól,</l><l n="53" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-53"> Bhi cnaimh-ruighead bachuird</l><l n="54" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-54"> Ar far ann gach sgìn aca;</l><l n="55" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-55"> Ag stabadh 'sa gearradh</l><l n="56" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-56"> Go leor, go leoir.</l><l n="57" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-57"> Ceád aithshlisne darach air,</l><l n="58" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-58"> Lasadh gabhail trìd na cheile;</l><l n="59" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-59"> Ag cnagadh, ag leagadh,<gap/></l><l n="60" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-60"> A bhodaigh as è mathairfe,</l><l n="61" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-61"> Chuir mainister na Búille suas,</l><l n="62" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-62"> 'Sligeach is Gailmhe is</l><l n="63" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-63"> Carruig Dhrum-Rùsga fòs.</l><l n="64" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-64"> Se Iarla Cilldara,</l><l n="65" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-65"> Agus Biatach Mhuighnealta,</l><l n="66" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-66"> Doil agus daltrom me</l><l n="67" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-67"> Fiosraidh do Mhoír.</l><l n="68" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-68"> Leagaidh an tamad sin,</l><l n="69" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-69"> Buáilidh an strámeàd sin,<hi rend="underline">Cick</hi> an sa tárr is<hi rend="underline">Cuff</hi> an sa tsróin.</l><l n="70" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-70"> Cia thoig an talarmfa?</l><l n="71" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-71"> Ar sa aon don eaglais,</l><l n="72" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-72"> Ag eirgihdh na sheasamh</l><l n="73" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-73"> 'Sa bagart go mór.</l><l n="74" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-74"> Ni hi an spiredis choisriogtha,</l><l n="75" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-75"> Bhi leis san racàn;</l><l n="76" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-76"> Acht bata maith, cnapànach,</l><l n="77" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-77"> Boglan dóirn.</l><l n="78" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-78"> Trath shaoil se na caibhliorr,</l><l n="79" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-79"> Alasgadh sdo thiórail;</l><l n="80" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-80"> Do faidgead an Sagart na mheall</l><l n="81" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-81"> Trasna faoi an mbórd.</l><l n="82" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-82"> Dirghe na braithre do thartail</l><l n="83" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-83"> Na braoine sin;</l><l n="84" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-84"> 'Sdo faigead an tathar gardian,</l><l n="85" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-85"> Ar athairr ansa graosacha.</l><l n="86" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-86"> Nuair abhi mise tall,</l><l n="87" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-87"> Aglacadh nan gradha,</l><l n="88" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-88"> Adhfocair an phapà,</l><l n="89" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-89"> Thall an sa Róimh.</l><l n="90" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-90"> Se an <hi rend="underline">Seven Wise Masters</hi>,</l><l n="91" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-91"> Bhi ar chluai sar a thar raige</l><l n="92" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-92"> Is é agithe bpotatuidh</l><l n="93" xml:id="spp-M63692D2-line-93"> Laimh le <hi rend="underline">Sheemór</hi>.M63692D2   </l></lg></div>
